<div id="c1">
<p>Of course, long ago Cosma Shalizi said all this <a href="http://www.cscs.umich.edu/~crshalizi/notebooks/faq.html#2.2" rel="nofollow">shorter and better</a>:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p><strong>Where do you find the time to read so much?</strong></p>
  
  <p>I don&#8217;t watch TV, I have no social life, and I read about a page a minute, if there isn&#8217;t any math to slow me down.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>&#8230;but then again, everything I write is just commentaries on off-hand remarks by Cosma.</p>

