<div id="c33">
<p>Any plans for what you&#8217;ll do with all that knowledge once you&#8217;ve finished accumulating it?</p>

<p>Reading a ton of books is not a goal that appeals to me.  I like learning as I do things, so I can apply knowledge right after picking it up.  If you read a book without having an application in mind for the information in it, you run the risk of never actually using that information.  (Of course there is also information in some books that you wouldn&#8217;t know to look for, though.)</p>

